Huds., Fl. Angl.: 39 (1762). Type Protologue: &quot;Habitat in cretaceis circa Rochester, Dartford and Gravesend, in Cantio&quot;. Type: United Kingdom. England: Kent, near Wye, grassland on chalk. 12 Jun. 1964, S.T. Blake 22178 (neotype, designated here: K [K000618780!]; isoneotype: BRI [BRI 252046 image!]). (Figure 4)
</paragraph>
